Elo, comes from the word connection.

When different elements come together, they tend to influence the entire universe, its paths, its stories, each element leaves its mark in time. 

This is a work that explores space and the connection between elements.

The piece has a few types of variations. Its pattern can follow 4 different formulas, where according to the values ​​such as speed, distance and frequency, it presents a certain result.

There are no predetermined color palettes, the code chooses the amount and colors that will be used, creating a very wide variety of combinations.

— 

Features:

- 6 background colors;
- 22 colors;
- 4 formulas;
- Light or Dark background;
- 1 to 6 colors combination;
- All colors mode;
- Tiles: 2 to 10;
- Margin: 5, 50, 100;
- Opacity: true/false;
- Limited space;
- There can be more than one color combination;

—

This artwork requires processing power and is intended for laptops and desktops primarily. It may take some time to render. 

- On Live mode press ’S’ to save in PNG;

October 2022 - @gpitombo

